{"tid":645557,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"判決鼓勵挺身而出　壯大#MeToo聲勢","createTime":"2018-04-28T08:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T08:54:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1f41569d5cef6cea466657b2392ca45351c3754d","tid":645557,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:42:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180428/20375255?_ga=2.104497920.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180428%2F20375255%3F_ga%3D2.104497920.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=w%2FpB5ZNj24SnWsdMZ3SEwoS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=1ecdca49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180428%2F20375255%3F_ga%3D2.104497920.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=2eb0dbee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180428/20375255?_ga=2.104497920.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年04月28日 <br />\n<br />\n判決鼓勵挺身而出　壯大#MeToo聲勢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180428/large/28wh102p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180428%2Flarge%2F28wh102p.jpg&h=196f3f1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■指控標哥士比性侵的女士為康斯坦德勝訴笑逐顏開。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標哥士比是#MeToo運動發揚光大後首位性侵罪成的名人，有女權律師認為，判決將鼓勵更多女性挺身而出，意味#MeToo運動或可進一步壯大。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n很多性侵指控不獲信任<br />\n<br />\n專攻性騷擾案的華盛頓律師卡茨（Debra Katz）認為，受害者與加害者對簿公堂需要極大勇氣，但此案「會鼓勵現時看到法律團隊之強大的其他女士」效發，反映「名人不會有（脫罪）通行證」。卡茨指#MeToo運動壯大前，很多女性的性侵指控都不獲信任，「尤其他們指控名人或有權力男士時」，但隨着女性更有勇氣發聲，社會風氣亦有改變。<br />\n<br />\n參與人權組織「美國公民自由聯盟」女權計劃的律師帕克（Sandra Park）認為，加害者代表律師將受害人妖魔化的策略過去管用，但#MeToo運動證明案件形式並不單一。<br />\n<br />\n美國多個女權組織已組成「適可而止」（enough is enough）聯盟，更在過去一周討論倡議立法解決性侵及性騷擾問題。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n美笑匠標哥士比　猥褻襲擊罪成　或要獄中度過餘生<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n蓬佩奧就任美國務卿　馬不停蹄外訪"},{"pid":"9ca3c9b8d210e57e55d4da8c24f40c7b2dc5f24f","tid":645557,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:54:40.000Z","msg":"#MeToo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}